## Development Rules

1. **Never send PII to any API** — client names, emails, phones stay in the browser
2. **Client IDs only in AI context** — system prompt, messages, tool payloads
3. **Name re-injection is local** — happens in browser or `/api/generate-file`
4. **localStorage keys use `conda_` prefix** — `conda_skill_files`, `conda_client_directory`, `conda_skill_banner_dismissed`
5. **All deliverables flow through chat** — no separate generation UI
6. **Skill files are templates, not style inputs** — Claude reads the actual document text and replicates structure
